"New stereo mix" is not really correct -- they are phased versions of the original stereo mix which has never been officially reissued. The information from Charly with regards to the mono mix is not useful nor accurate (the original stereo mix also has double-tracked vocals on Levitation, for example), so it should be removed. This label has claimed several documented falsehoods.
